ownersListingProfile.aboutYou: Our family is a resident of Kefalonia. We love the island and are happy to share with you this love!
ownersListingProfile.whyHere:
We built and decorated the cottages with sincere diligence, trying to convey to you our joy of your stay with us.
We hope, you will love cute Spartia beaches that offer clear, warm waters and picturesque coastline. 
All this beauty is just 2 min walk from the cottages.
ownersListingProfile.uniqueBenefits: We offer charming, quiet environment, home atmosphere, true Greek hospitality - come and enjoy!

Our main goal is a satisfied customer- before, during and after using our services. We are committed to finding and managing a pleasant stay for our customers in the destination of choice. The agency supports the client from the moment they submit a booking till the end of their stay.

Along with personal recommendations for the local area, a bespoke service and - if the mood takes you - extra home comforts (airport pick-up, fridge fill and babysitting to name a few), Veeve has mastered a way to help guests live like Londoners.

Characterful homes. Dedicated service. Memorable stays.

ownersListingProfile.uniqueBenefits: No smoking, pets and parties! Please note there are 2 airbeds available, a single and a double to sleep a total of 10 people.
